title: Strictly Come Dancing: week seven  results – live
summary: Vicky Pattison dazzled with a top-scoring tango, while Balvinder Sopal added a vibrant Bollywood touch to the competition. La Voix struggled with a disappointing foxtrot, landing at the bottom of the leaderboard. The midway point of the contest raises questions about who will be eliminated next.

title: NFL week 10: Bucs v Patriots, Vikings v Ravens, Colts edge Falcons in Berlin and more – live
summary: Seven NFL games are set to start at 6 PM UK time following the Indianapolis Colts' overtime victory over the Atlanta Falcons. Jonathan Taylor scored the decisive touchdown for the Colts. Fans can look forward to an exciting lineup of matches.

title: Guardiola thanks Doku and Manchester City for ‘present’ of Liverpool victory
summary: Pep Guardiola celebrated his 1,000th match as a manager in a clash against Liverpool. Liverpool's manager, Arne Slot, expressed frustration over Virgil van Dijk's disallowed goal during the game. The match highlighted contrasting emotions for the two coaches.

title: Wales humbled by Argentina as Steve Tandy witnesses scale of task ahead
summary: Wales captain Jac Morgan suffered a dislocated shoulder in the team's 52-28 loss to Argentina. The injury raises concerns about his availability for upcoming matches. The defeat marks a challenging moment for the Welsh side in their campaign.

title: Trump weighs giving Americans $2,000 from tariff revenues in bid for support
summary: Former President Trump has proposed a plan that he suggests may require congressional approval to be implemented. This idea aligns with his previous suggestions on similar issues. Approval from Congress will be crucial for the plan's execution.
